title: Pixel 3a does not Boot. "Locked Bootloader"
content:
Hello All,

Bought a Pixel 3a off ebay.
The device came with Android Q Beta. 
I tried to enable developers mode in order to Flash an recent build of Q OTA.

Rebooted the device now it doesn't boot.

Error is it cant find OS.

I cant get into recovery mode.  But i can get into fastboot. 
Is there anything else i can try to do to restore the device?

Unfortunately Fastboot command are very limited since the boot loader is locked.
